<div class="panel panel--collapse {% if active %}panel--collapse-in{% endif %}">
  <div class="panel__header">
    <h3 class="panel__title">Video settings</h3>
    <span class="panel__title-hint hint">(Optional - Recommended)</span>
    <a class="panel__collapse-btn {% if active == false %}collapsed{% endif %}" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse-2" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne"></a>
  </div>
  <div class="collapse {% if active %}show{% endif %}" id="collapse-2">
    <div class="panel__body">
      <form>
        <div class="panel__section">
          <div class="form-group">
            <h5 class="form-group__title">
              Video episode titles
            </h5>

            <div class="help-block help-block--tip help-block--inline">
              <p class="hint">
                The video episode title will be autogenerated from your RSS feed. You can add addtional
                text in front or/and at the end of your titles below.
              </p>

              <p class="hint">
                <span class="help-block__label">Tip</span>
                We recommend to add the name of your show or company to increase discoverability.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-6">
                <label for="prepend-titles">Prepend video titles</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="prepend-titles"></input>
              </div>
              <div class="col-6">
                <label for="append-titles">Append video titles</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="append-titles"></input>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="panel__block">
            <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
              <span class="form-check__pre-inline-text">Preview:</span>
              <label class="form-check-label">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="preview-type" value="long" checked>
                <span class="form-check-input-appearance"></span>
                Longest title
              </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
              <label class="form-check-label">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="preview-type" value="short">
                <span class="form-check-input-appearance"></span>
                Shortest title
              </label>
            </div>

            <p class="text">
              <span class="text__highlighted">The Music Makers â€“</span>
              033 How Did It Become OK For People To Be Late For Everything?
              <span class="text__highlighted">Articles That...</span>
            </p>

            <p class="text">
              <span class="text__highlighted">100</span>/100 characters used
              <a class="tooltip-block tooltip-block--inline" type="button" data-toggle="tooltip"
                 data-placement="top"
                 title="YouTube limits the title length to 100 characters. We'll limit it to 100 characters for you, but don't get too wordy or it could be truncated.">
                {{mixins.svg('help')}}
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel__section">
          <div class="form-group">
            <h5 class="form-group__title">
              Video description
            </h5>
            <div class="form-check">
              <label class="form-check-label">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="settings-radio" id="settings-radio-1" value="custom" checked>
                <span class="form-check-input-appearance"></span>
                Custom
                <span class="hint">
                  - your custom description will appear on all your episodes
                </span>
              </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check">
              <label class="form-check-label">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="settings-radio" id="settings-radio-1" value="summary">
                <span class="form-check-input-appearance"></span>
                Summary
              </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check">
              <label class="form-check-label">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="settings-radio" id="settings-radio-1" value="full">
                <span class="form-check-input-appearance"></span>
                Full description
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="description-textarea">Custom video description</label>
            <a href="#" class="link link--inline pull-right">Preview example</a>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="description-textarea"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="help-block help-block--tip">
            <p class="hint">
              <span class="help-block__label">Tip</span>
              If you'd like to add a call-to-action, we recommend putting it in this box, so it shows
              up in your description.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-6">
            <div class="form-group form-group--last-with-hint">
              <label for="playlist">
                Select video category
                <span class="required-text">(required)</span>
              </label>

              <select id="playlist" class="form-control">
                <option value="" disabled selected>Choose your category</option>
                <option>Category 1</option>
                <option>Category 2</option>
                <option>Category 3</option>
              </select>

              <div class="help-block form-group__help form-group__help--right">
                {{mixins.svg('info')}}
                <p class="hint">
                  YouTube requires a category, and we've listed them all here. The categories are exceedingly
                  broad and don't matter that much.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
